The following are the captains of the contingent going to the 37th Inter IIT Aquatics Meet to be held at IIT Gandhinagar from 4th to 8th October 2023.

Contingent Captain: Prama Adhya
Women's Swimming Captain: Pravalika Das
Men's Swimming Captain: Chethan Girish
Waterpolo Captain: Priyansh Shrivastava
Waterpolo Vice Captain: Sparsh Burman

The Scholars' Avenue wishes good luck to the contingent representing IIT Kharagpur.

To help everyone sitting for placements this year, The Scholars' Avenue presents TnPedia 2023, a compilation of information of 130+ companies and profiles from those who've gone through the process and wanted to share their experiences. It includes details about the process and preparation tips to help the batches to come. We are thankful to everyone who took out some time and shared the information.

Link: https://bit.ly/tnpedia23

text:
Hello!

We, at The Scholars' Avenue, are a bunch of KGPians focused on ending world hunger, poverty and crime through the dissemination of news, satire and comics on campus. We're hoping to recruit folks who're looking to explore similar interests and hang out with a fun group of people. We will be conducting an introductory seminar on 1st September followed by selections from 2nd to 4th.

Fill out this form to apply: https://forms.gle/C4pHu55giToQG2Jv6
